<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <h4>MY APP❤️</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      {{#if user }}
        <li><a href="/profile">Profile</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a></li>
      {{else}}
        <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
        <li><a href="/signup">Signup</a></li>
      {{/if}}
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <h1 class="display-4">Login Project</h1>
      <p class="lead">This is a simple project to show user registration and login.</p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      <p>
         <li>API 1:-

            signup/user <br>

            Middleware 1- Validator (Email,FirstName,LastName,PhoneNo,Password) <br>

            Middleware 2- Route Handler {
            Check if Email is in database = respone(error)
            else - Create Entry = response(success)
            }
         </li>
         <li>
            API 2:-

            login/user<br>

            1 - Email and Password = response(sucess,error)<br>
            2 - Access Token
          
          </li>
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="#" role="button">Learn more</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-J6qa4849blE2+poT4WnyKhv5vZF5SrPo0iEjwBvKU7imGFAV0wwj1yYfoRSJoZ+n" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>